![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c07229ef-f9bc-489a-97d0-d27de7882c27/20240907_170548.jpg?format=original)

*   ## MJF DEF. DANIEL GARCIA
    

The story of this match is both men are trying to break each other's necks. Simple stuff. MJF attacks the wound from the champagne bottle on Dynamite to bust Garcia open. MJF tries to tombstone Garcia off the top rope again but Garcia reversed into a sick DDT.

MJF spits a nasty loogie into Garcia’s face. This baits Garcia into a rage again giving MJF the upper hand.

Great back and forth until MJF puts Garcia in a Walls of Jericho, a reference to both of their history with Jericho. Garcia reversed into a Yes Lock which could be taken as both a reference to both of their wins over Bryan AND the fact that maybe Garcia should've went with Bryan instead of Jericho.

MJF lowblows Garcia and rolls him up for the win.

MJF tries to shake Garcia's hand and go for the low blow again. Garcia is prepared. He lowblows MJF.

Takes him to the corner. Spits in his face and PILEDRIVER OFF THE TOP ROPE TO MJF.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/72f32d0b-82b4-44ad-a0a9-7ec95f06891c/20240907_173224.jpg?format=original)

