![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6cfe9c68-0759-40f2-b740-701d09ebd3bb/20240907_202541.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_LIGHTS OUT STEEL CAGE MATCH: HANGMAN PAGE VS SWERVE STRICKLAND_**
    

Hangman comes out with Barbed Wire around his fist. Swerve is out with the memory of his burned down childhood home on his gear.

They begin to try and DECAPITATE each other with the still lowering cage. Prince Nana shoves both men into the ring because they would not give.

StapleGun is introduced. Swerve is immune to staples when his adrenaline is pumping so he takes the stapler from Hangman and STAPLES PHOTOS OF HIS FAMILY ONTO HANGMAN'S FACE.

Hangman is able to take the advantage again when he realizes the cage won't allow him to hit his Buckshot Lariat

This was possibly one of the most violent steel cage matches in modern pro wrestling history.

Hangman and Swerve displayed nothing but pure hatred for each other. Chairs, cinderblocks, staples and even NEEDLES.

In the end, Hangman hits Swerve with an INCREDIBLE chair shot to the head that tenders him unconscious and ends the match via KO.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/03bca0f1-1fb4-44cf-ab8a-dc1e0cd59f08/20240907_203131.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4fcbbae5-f9b0-4609-8dd6-7b1c1b224659/Screenshot_20240907_205008.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d61a5be6-3e2b-46b5-8474-dad1f75c0fee/20240907_205234.jpg?format=original)